lyrics: Intro
Dil se, aradhana karoon main
Is zubaan se, naam tera hi loon main
Poore dil se, aradhana karoon main
Is zubaan se, naam tera hi loon main
Pre Chorus
Karta hoon tera shukriya main prabhu
Karta hoon tera shukriya main
Chorus
Tere fazal mein, teri daya mein
Lipta main rehta hoon
Verse 1
Jab hota hoon, bechain kabhi
Teri ruh tab mujhko thamti hai
Meri mushkilon mein,
Har ek dard aur gham mein
Khudawand tu hi, mera shaafi hai
Verse 2
Jab leta hoon, main naam tera
Teri samarth ko tab main dekhta hoon
Tujhse mili, har barkat mujhe
Mehfooz tere sang main rehta hoon
